Calculating the Manhattan distance heuristic for A* coordinates:

```cpp
#include <cmath>

struct FIntPoint {
    int X, Y;
};

// Manhattan distance is ideal for grid-based orthogonal movement
int CalculateHeuristic(FIntPoint Current, FIntPoint Destination) {
    return std::abs(Current.X - Destination.X) + std::abs(Current.Y - Destination.Y);
}
```
